## 2. Brand Identity & Design Tokens

### Color Palette (Hex Reference)

Use Tailwind classes for solids (e.g., `text-forvis-blue-600`), inline styles for exact hex matching if tokens are missing.

**Primary Blue:**
- `#2E5AAC` - Brand Core
- `#1C3667` - Deep/Header
- `#5B93D7` - Highlight

**Gold Accent:**
- `#C7B179` - Primary Gold
- `#88815E` - Dark Gold

**Backgrounds:**
- `#F0F7FD` - Lightest Blue
- `#F8F9FA` - Gray-50
- `#FFFFFF` - White

**Text:**
- `#212529` - Headings
- `#343A40` - Body
- `#6C757D` - Muted

### Gradient Registry (Inline Styles Required)

**Do not use Tailwind utilities for gradients.** Copy these exact strings to ensure brand consistency.

#### A. Primary Surfaces (Headers, CTAs)

```javascript
// Diagonal Blue (Standard Headers/Buttons)
style={{ background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #5B93D7 0%, #2E5AAC 50%, #1C3667 100%)' }}

// Horizontal Blue (Table Headers)
style={{ background: 'linear-gradient(to right, #2E5AAC, #25488A)' }}
```

#### B. Dashboard Interaction

```javascript
// Base Card Background (Light)
style={{ background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #F0F7FD 0%, #E0EDFB 100%)' }}

// Hover Overlay Effect (RGBA)
style={{ background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(91, 147, 215, 0.06) 0%, rgba(46, 90, 172, 0.08) 100%)' }}
```

#### C. Premium/Executive (Gold Accents)

```javascript
// Gold Premium (Shared Services, High Value)
style={{ background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #C7B179 0%, #88815E 100%)' }}

// Blue-to-Gold (Executive Dashboards/Partner View)
style={{ background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #5B93D7 0%, #2E5AAC 50%, #C7B179 100%)' }}
```

#### D. Workspaces (Data Heavy)

```javascript
// Warm/Paper (Lists & Forms - Extended Usage)
style={{ 
  background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #F0EAE0 0%, #E0D5C3 100%)', 
  borderColor: '#C9BCAA' 
}}
```

