## 5. Professional Polish & Accessibility

### Transitions
Apply `transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out` to all interactive elements.

### Focus States (MANDATORY for accessibility)
```typescript
className="focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-forvis-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
```

### Contrast
Ensure text on Blue/Gold gradients is always `text-white`.

### Shadows
- **Static elements:** `shadow-corporate`
- **Hover states:** `shadow-corporate-md`

### Mobile First
Default to `flex-col` or `grid-cols-1`, expanding at `md:` breakpoints.

