## Common Mistakes to Avoid

❌ **Don't** use black text on gradient backgrounds.

❌ **Don't** mix "Gold" and "Blue" randomly. Gold is reserved for Premium/Shared Services/Partner contexts.

❌ **Don't** hardcode padding pixels. Use Tailwind scale (`p-4`, `p-6`).

❌ **Don't** create new button styles. If the Button component doesn't fit, the design is wrong.

